remarks.para:
For example, if you want to change the color to red, just surround original text with \e statements:

static string replacer(string str, Step step)
    => step.DifficultyLevel == DifficultyLevel.Nightmare ? $"\e[38;2;255;0;0m{str}\e[0m" : str;

By design of  and  types,
emit text should be formatted as follows:
RecordType { Property1 = Value1, Property2 = Value2, Property3 = { NestedProperty = Value3 } }

						The suggested implementation is like this:
						private bool PrintMembers(StringBuilder builder)
{
    builder.Append($"{nameof(Property1)} = {Property1}");
    builder.Append(", ");
    builder.Append($"{nameof(Property2)} = {Property2}");
    builder.Append(", ");
    builder.Append($"{nameof(Property3)} = {{ {Property3} }}");
    return true;
}

